  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tbsp of vegetable oil in a large terracotta vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chopped dandelion greens, turmeric, coriander, black pepper, and flaky salt. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the Ethiopian lardons and cook until heated through, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and drizzle with truffle oil.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional dandelion greens if desired."
